10 a warrant or detainer;
11 5. Inmates returning to community supervision from an
12 intermediate revocation facility; and
13 6. Inmates that the Department determines would be physically
14 or mentally unable to return to the workforce upon release from
15 incarceration.
16 E. The Department of Corrections is authorized to promulgate
17 rules and procedures to implement the provisions of this section.
